<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1362] Publish sources and javadoc jars</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1362</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently just binaries jars get published on Maven Central (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/kafka/kafka_2.10/0.8.1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/kafka/kafka_2.10/0.8.1/&lt;/a&gt; ). Please also publish sources and javadoc jars.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12706941">KAFKA-1362</key>
            <summary>Publish sources and javadoc jars</summary>
